--[[
[================]
M_Supply_Caravans_STOGETHER.script
Description: Dynamic Economy, Supply Caravans, and closed-loop NPC Loot & Trade system.
Written for Anomaly Together multiplayer.

Systems:
 - Supply Caravans   : periodically spawns A-Life supply squads walking between bases on set routes.
 - Dynamic Economy   : monitors caravan squad survival; arrival triggers trader price drops & premium stock injection;
                       destruction triggers inflation & physical item shortages.
 - Trade Patching    : dynamically intercepts trade_manager buy/sell discounts to adjust trader pricing.
 - Stock Management  : iterates over trader inventory upon opening dialogue to physically purge scarce items or
                       inject premium restocks in real-time.
 - Grassroots Trade  : NPCs scan inventories for essential survival items (medkits, bandages, food, drinks);
                       when in need, they buy from nearby base traders or campfire friendly peers.
 - Loot Selling Loop : NPCs scan inventories for looted monster parts or weapons; sell them to base traders
                       for rubles to finance their survival needs.
 - Out of Stock Alert: PDA alerts fired when an NPC buys the last item of a category from a base trader.
 - Persistence       : deterministic actor_on_save / actor_on_load binary packet saving of level economy states.
[================]
--]]

